RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', EmulatedDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', EmulatedDevice.DeviceCount AS 'Device Count', OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.MatchedPacketCount AS 'Matched Packet Count', OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.NotMatchedPacketCount AS 'Not Matched Packet Count', OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.TxPacketOutCount AS 'PacketOut Count' FROM AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, Port, OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults, OpenflowControllerProtocolConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND OpenflowControllerProtocolConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.ParentHnd = OpenflowControllerProtocolConfig.Handle AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND OpenflowControllerProtocolConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) UNION SELECT ExternalDevicePort.Name AS 'Port Name', EmulatedDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', EmulatedDevice.DeviceCount AS 'Device Count', OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.MatchedPacketCount AS 'Matched Packet Count', OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.NotMatchedPacketCount AS 'Not Matched Packet Count', OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.TxPacketOutCount AS 'PacketOut Count' FROM AllDevice AS EmulatedDevice, ExternalDevicePort, OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults, Port, OpenflowControllerProtocolConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND OpenflowControllerProtocolConfig.ParentHnd = EmulatedDevice.Handle AND OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.ParentHnd = OpenflowControllerProtocolConfig.Handle AND EmulatedDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND ExternalDevicePort.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND OpenflowReactiveModeAggregateResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND
